that I'm interested in.

562
00:29:06,060 --> 00:29:07,060
Just kidding.

563
00:29:08,020 --> 00:29:09,660
I know you came to save me today.

564
00:29:10,660 --> 00:29:11,300
Yeah.

565
00:29:12,540 --> 00:29:13,140
Sit.

566
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:16,940
You always think of me

567
00:29:16,940 --> 00:29:18,060
and take care of me.

568
00:29:18,540 --> 00:29:19,700
