573
00:29:25,460 --> 00:29:26,340
It was fine, actually.

574
00:29:27,020 --> 00:29:28,100
If you weren't here today,

575
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,460
I couldn't have saved them both.

576
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:31,340
Yeah.

577
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:35,260
You and I could each save one.

578
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:46,460
I'll tell you a secret.

579
00:29:47,620 --> 00:29:48,260
What?

580
00:29:50,060 --> 00:29:51,820
Actually, the one you saved today

581
00:29:53,300 --> 00:29:54,340
was the one I wanted to save.

582
00:29:58,780 --> 00:29:59,500
Your Highness,

583
00:29:59,860 --> 00:30:00,940
do you mean it?

584
00:30:03,660 --> 00:30:05,900
That girl is witty and intelligent.

585
00:30:06,620 --> 00:30:08,620
You and she make a good couple.

586
00:30:11,780 --> 00:30:13,020
This is good.

587
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:14,460
In the palace,

588
00:30:15,940 --> 00:30:17,380
you can take good care of her.

589
00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:20,420
Hear me out.

590
00:30:21,460 --> 00:30:22,420
Here is what I think.

591
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:24,580
From now on,

592
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:26,660
everything about her in the palace

593
00:30:27,620 --> 00:30:28,860
will be my responsibility.

594
00:30:31,980 --> 00:30:32,620
What do you think?

595
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:36,940
What is this?

596
00:30:40,140 --> 00:30:41,740
It is goji berry and ginger soup I made.

597
00:30:42,020 --> 00:30:42,820
The water was cold.

598
00:30:43,060 --> 00:30:44,620
Drink some to stay warm.

599
00:30:44,620 --> 00:30:45,340
You made it for me?

600
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:46,540
Of course.

601
00:30:47,180 --> 00:30:48,060
You are the one who treats me the best.

602
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:48,820
Let's share it.

603
00:30:51,460 --> 00:30:52,100
Don't move.

604
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:53,820
Move again and I'll yell.

605
00:30:54,180 --> 00:30:55,980
Let go, Shen Feixue.

606
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:58,340
How do you know my name?

607
00:30:58,740 --> 00:31:00,620
I don't just know your name.

608
00:31:00,900 --> 00:31:03,260
I also know you always hurt yourself
when doing embroidery.

609
00:31:03,260 --> 00:31:04,740
You break strings
when playing the guqin.

610
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:06,540
You cheat in card games.

611
00:31:06,540 --> 00:31:08,660
- Only when shopping for jewelry,
- I...

612
00:31:08,660 --> 00:31:10,220
you will be excited.

613
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:12,660
How do you know all this?

614
00:31:12,980 --> 00:31:14,500
A daughter knows her mother well.

615
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:16,020
Who is your mother?

616
00:31:16,620 --> 00:31:17,380
Tell me.

617
00:31:17,460 --> 00:31:18,740
Where did you hide my Shan?

618
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:20,500
If you don't tell me,

619
00:31:20,500 --> 00:31:21,300
I'll look for her myself.

620
00:31:23,340 --> 00:31:24,100
Shan.

621
00:31:25,220 --> 00:31:26,020
Shan.

622
00:31:26,220 --> 00:31:27,020
Shan.

623
00:31:27,180 --> 00:31:27,940
Shan.

624
00:31:31,380 --> 00:31:32,260
Can your daughter

625
00:31:32,260 --> 00:31:33,660
fit into such a small cabinet?

626
00:31:37,260 --> 00:31:38,580
What if

627
00:31:38,620 --> 00:31:40,660
you've cut her into pieces
and hidden her in there?

628
00:31:41,260 --> 00:31:42,060
Let go, Shen Feixue.

629
00:31:42,060 --> 00:31:43,100
Give me my daughter.

630
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:44,060
Do you know

631
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:45,340
that kidnapping is a felony?

632
00:31:46,220 --> 00:31:48,300
The Empress arrives.

633
00:31:51,900 --> 00:31:53,140
Her Majesty is here.

634
00:31:53,540 --> 00:31:54,540
What a coincidence.

635
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:56,700
I don't even have to go to her.

636
00:31:57,380 --> 00:31:58,500
We'll see.

637
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:03,980
If you're really worried
about your daughter,

638
00:32:03,980 --> 00:32:05,060
don't say anything.

639
00:32:05,340 --> 00:32:06,540
What do you mean by that?

640
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,420
I...

641
00:32:08,420 --> 00:32:09,300
Your daughter

642
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:11,300
openly brought me into the palace

643
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:12,500
and left her room at night.

644
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:14,620
She didn't even show up
when her mother came to visit her.

645
00:32:14,820 --> 00:32:16,620
If the Empress finds out...

646
00:32:17,780 --> 00:32:19,220
Why did she bring you here?

647
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:22,300
Are you threatening her with something?

648
00:32:23,460 --> 00:32:24,900
Deal with the Empress first.

649
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:31,460
Greetings, Your Majesty.

650
00:32:31,860 --> 00:32:32,780
I'm sorry

651
00:32:32,780 --> 00:32:34,140
that I didn't go out to welcome you.

652
00:32:34,180 --> 00:32:35,580
Please forgive me.

653
00:32:36,180 --> 00:32:37,500
What are you doing here?

654
00:32:37,500 --> 00:32:38,620
Your Majesty,

655
00:32:38,780 --> 00:32:41,500
I heard today
that my daughter fell into the water.

656
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:43,260
I'm really worried.

657
00:32:43,380 --> 00:32:45,740
So I'm here to see her.

658
00:32:45,780 --> 00:32:48,220
I also came to visit her because I heard

659
00:32:48,260 --> 00:32:49,420
Miss Mei fell into the water.

660
00:32:50,620 --> 00:32:52,500
You making time to visit my daughter

661
00:32:52,660 --> 00:32:54,620
makes me very grateful.

662
00:32:55,460 --> 00:32:57,820
It's just that she got a cold

663
00:32:57,980 --> 00:32:59,460
and can't get up to meet you.

664
00:32:59,780 --> 00:33:01,460
Please forgive her.

665
00:33:02,100 --> 00:33:02,900
She's ill?

666
00:33:06,780 --> 00:33:07,660
She's faking it.

667
00:33:08,060 --> 00:33:09,820
The one in Yao's room must have been

668
00:33:09,940 --> 00:33:11,060
Mei Yushan.

669
00:33:12,180 --> 00:33:13,660
Once she gets better,

670
00:33:13,860 --> 00:33:15,260
she'll definitely go
to the Huacai Hall to...

671
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:16,660
I'm already here.

672
00:33:16,660 --> 00:33:17,540
I need to see her

673
00:33:17,580 --> 00:33:18,860
and talk to her.

674
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:20,060
Only then can I rest assured.

675
00:33:20,060 --> 00:33:20,860
Your Majesty.

676
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:22,460
I'm afraid she'll infect you.

677
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:23,140
Your Majesty.

678
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:33,390
♪It's your mesmerizing glance♪

679
00:33:33,710 --> 00:33:36,980
♪Freezing the gentle breeze
of the mundane world♪

680
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:42,610
♪Your gentle call awakens me
from my unfinished dreams♪

681
00:33:42,610 --> 00:33:46,260
♪It's hard to convey my love for you
when fighting for the homeland♪

682
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:49,780
♪Our destined encounter♪

683
00:33:49,780 --> 00:33:54,640
♪I am meant to accompany you
on this journey♪

684
00:33:55,090 --> 00:33:58,160
♪Wishing for a bit more♪

685
00:33:58,290 --> 00:34:01,870
♪So love feels even more real♪

686
00:34:01,870 --> 00:34:07,510
♪You and I, each completing the other,
year after year♪

687
00:34:07,510 --> 00:34:10,530
♪Accompany me to explore the world♪

688
00:34:10,530 --> 00:34:14,180
♪We walk together on bustling streets♪

689
00:34:14,370 --> 00:34:19,550
♪My heart leans
towards your warm embrace♪

690
00:34:19,750 --> 00:34:26,530
♪We're both kites reclaimed
from the edge of the sky♪

691
00:34:26,660 --> 00:34:32,110
♪If it's an unfathomable fate,
let me do it again♪

692
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:38,570
♪We're both misunderstood,
yet we accept it willingly♪

693
00:34:39,020 --> 00:34:47,850
♪Step forth boldly and join me
without asking where we're heading♪
